 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x114e",
   "jp_len": 143,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "{00}ゃ{00}か{00}ィ{00}げ{00}ッ{00}わ{00}分{00}オ{00}招？{00}D{00}く{00}ザ{00}ふ{00}者{00}ぞ{00}ル{00}ゥ{00}来{00}そ{00}ュ{00}ウ{00}Sぁあいうえおダチッツテ{01}デ、トドナ。つネハバパ·々ビブベミメちっぞャー（ルでロど縛ぬ縛回艦気球るカね{00}·{00}！な{01}Mニうな、{00}{01}！ミ{00}Mあいな、{00}{01}ぁ哦……明明不是Turn系机体、竟有这{00}般力量……",
   "zh_hex": ""
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x11dd",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……有趣！你们这帮家伙、实在是太有趣{00}了！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7cbea82ef97e7b8e7bbe7b9e910e7dfe7fd02e87fef29e7b6e86ae7cbea8200e7baef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x120f",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你说有趣！？拿性命相搏的战斗、你居然{00}说它有趣！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7ede7cbea82ef9705e9a7e951e853e8b1ed6ce7b4ef28e7ff02e7b8ea4ce7ef00e7ede978e7cbea82ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1248",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈哈！不错、小妞！！你就是海盗头目{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97e7b5e88502e83eefe1ef97ef97e7b8e7c5e7b6e91be9f3e92eefd400050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1265",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比起迪安娜那帮人、跟你打可有意思多了{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e847ea11e7fce7eae7b7e910b402e973e7b8e7f5e7c4e7cbef3ca6e7e9e7ba00060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x127d",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "果然、就这样在这里分出胜负、太可惜了{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e871e7ef02e7c5e7b9e7daef29e7b9ef31efaeefbee8dbe92c02e86ae7c4e9c8e7ba00ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12af",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12d2",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "反正你们也打算去投靠那艘大天使号的吧{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15e87cef3be7b8e7bbe7c0e7f5e889e7ebe948e8c7e7b7eb18efa5e844e83fe833e7b4e7d000050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12ef",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、这场胜负就留到那时再分吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7b9e876e8dbe92ce7c5e98ce7d7e7b7ef2de80bcde7d006000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1326",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这到底是怎么回事……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7d7e9b4e7b6e7f2e7bdef52efb809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1357",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您就是大天使号的拉米亚斯舰长吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7c5e7b6efa5e844e83fe833e7b4e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef34e7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1368",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那台叫∀的机体、已经由我们替你们夺回{00}来了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ea16e8c1effee7b4e7e4ef4f02ef3ae8b7e8a6efcce7bbea50e7b8e7bbea17ef5200efcfe7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x139e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bb09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13c2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们是十字先锋",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b6ea4ae980ef8be9670000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13d0",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……宇宙海盗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8bee8bfe91be9f30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x140a",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "十字先锋啊……你们、就是那个宇宙海盗{00}……来着？",
   "zh_hex": "15ea4ae980ef8be967e7c30909e7b8e7bb02e7c5e7b6e7b7e828e8bee8bfe91be9f3000909efcfe86d050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1443",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "宇宙海盗吗……不过、十字先锋这名号、{00}我倒是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bee8bfe91be9f3e8020909e7b5ef3602ea4ae980ef8be967e7b9e8ace8330200efcce848e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x145a",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我记得、那应该是布霍·康采恩组建的私{00}人军队才对……？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce996e80a02e7b7e873e898e7b6e831ebfeef4beb57ec9ee7eeea0dea61e7b4efd500efb2e7e0e7c9e836e7be0909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1495",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x149c",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "十字先锋、是我的祖父麦兹亚·罗纳他、",
   "zh_hex": "15ea4ae980ef8be96702e7b6efcce7b4ebe1e888ec43e856e7d6ef4be7ece882e80c020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14b5",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为了建立宇宙巴比伦尼亚、而一手组建起{00}来的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7baea61e86be8bee8bfe85be825ea5be896e7d602e89c87aeea0dea61e84700d9e7b40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14e7",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我听说、麦兹亚·罗纳是个贵族主义的忠{00}实信奉者",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8d1e7ed02ec43e856e7d6ef4be7ece882e7b6e828e930eb5ee954e8cee7b4ec1800e87fe90feac1ef6e0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1505",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么说来、你们的思想、比起我们应该更{00}接近提坦斯和新吉翁才对",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bde7edd902e7b8e7bbe7b4a6e7e602e825e8478be7bbe873e898e95200b796e821e843e7c8e7d3ef8ae7d9ee88e836e7be00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1526",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那又为何、要来协助我们？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8f1e7c1efbc02ef2aefcfe8f6ea23efcce7bb050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1551",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自从贝拉继承了祖父的事业、十字先锋就{00}已经变了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e88ae857e7c2e9d6ea75e7baebe1e888e7b4efb8eada02ea4ae980ef8be967e7c500ef3ae8b7e955e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x158a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你是？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8e7b6050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15ad",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度·纳乌、海盗高达X1的驾驶员",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96def4be882e94d02e91be9f3e812ef2beed9eff7e7b4e953e975e8490000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15db",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度……你应该还有别的名字吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96d0909e7b8e873e898e7f7e7cbe7e5e7b4e8ace980e7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1618",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "克瓦特罗·巴吉纳这名字、我看不怎么适{00}合你啊？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d5e99fe7cfe7ec04e85be7d9e882e7b9e8ace980028be7f6e7b5e7f2e7bdef4100a0e7b8e7c3050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1657",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1668",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1669",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001063c00136e1833020001061b001316173302000115e82fef29e7b4efcc02e7c5e7b6e902e95fe96def4be882e94d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x168f",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "倒也不是说、我就仅仅是这么个身份而已{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e848e7c0e7b5e7b6e7ed02efcce7c5eb7aeb7ae7b6e7b9e7bde828e88dea22e89cef3a0009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16ac",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但至少、我决意要成为贝拉的力量、这一{00}点是事实",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe897b1028be8abef3cef2ae837e7c1e857e7c2e7b4dae85102e7b98700e822e7b6a9e87f00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16c5",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉的愿望、是打倒地球圈的敌人、并不{00}是为了散播贵族主义",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2e7b4e961e96502e7b6e7f5e848ef63efd3e9fbe7b4e7e3efb202e957e7b500e7b6e7c1e7baef68ed70e930eb5ee954e8ce0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16ea",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "至少这一点、还请你相信",
   "zh_hex": "15e897eface7b9efb6e82202e7f7e83ae7b8e8b1e90f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1736",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、他们也的确把∀给夺回来了",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602e80ce7bbe7c0e7b4e88ce81beffee839ea17ef52efcfe7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x174b",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要是我们的敌人、哪会这么做？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b6efcce7bbe7b4e7e3efb202e8ffe7e2e7b9e7bde81c050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x178a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……确实如此",
   "zh_hex": "150909e88ce87fe7f0e7ca0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17b7",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么……你就是十字先锋的贝拉·罗纳、{00}对吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd0909e7b8e7c5e7b6ea4ae980ef8be967e7b4e857e7c2ef4be7ece8820200e7bee7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17d2",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们说、是为了打倒敌人而行动、可是…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7ed02e7b6e7c1e7bae7f5e848e7e3efb2e89cefd6ef3002e7c4e7b60900090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x180e",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们真正的敌人、目前都还没有开始行动",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe820ef3be7b4e7e3efb202efd4ef51e840e7f7e7d8e7cbe7fae908efd6ef300000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x183b",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个敌人、究竟是谁？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e828e7e3efb202e906ef2ce7b6e923050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1862",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "现在不能说、说了也没人信",
   "zh_hex": "15e82fef29e7b5e7c6e7ed02e7ede7bae7c0e7d8efb2e90f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1898",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比起那些、我认为眼下当务之急、是与各{00}位协力、平定地球圈的混乱",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e847e7b7e8a4028be8a0e7c1e90b89c4e94fe7cdea6202e7b6e832e81900e834e8f6da02e887e867bf95e9fbe7b4ea41e9760000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18db",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18fd",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我看不妨答应下来、克瓦特罗大尉",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7f6e7b5e97fea96e873ef4defcf02e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1914",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我觉得、这些人和我们的目的其实是一致{00}的、",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8aee80a02e7b9e8a4efb2e7d3efcce7bbe7b4efd4e7b4e8cfe87fe7b6efb6ea3200e7b4020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x192f",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "既然如此、我觉得彼此相互协力、不是更{00}好吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c4e7efe7f0e7ca02efcce8aee80aefc9e7cae8b1e9f9e8f6efb002e7b5e7b6e95200e7c7e8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1963",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……说得也是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7ede80ae7c0e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x196c",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么贝拉·罗纳……你们的这番提议、我{00}就心怀感激地接受了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bde857e7c2ef4be7ece8820909e7b8e7bbe7b4e7b9ee6de821e8e302efcc00e7c5e82deb03e87de9b9ef63efcee8c8e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19a6",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好的、今后还请多多关照",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c7e7b402efb9e7fee7f7e83ae7e9e7e9e8bbea1a0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19cc",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是阿斯兰·萨拉吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7d2e7c8e86fef4be83be7c2e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19f5",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是、他是帕特里克·萨拉议长之子、本在{00}执行机密任务……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b602e80ce7b6eb01e7cfef31e7d5ef4be83be7c2e8e3ef34e7cde88602efa6ef2900e9fcefd6e7e4e9bde89ae94f09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a17",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "据地面传来的情报、他似乎一直和大天使{00}号一同行动……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ccef63e862ea38efcfe7b4e88be91302e80ce944e933efb6e875e7d3efa5e844e83f00e833efb6e85defd6ef3009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a55",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "大天使号……",
   "zh_hex": "15efa5e844e83fe83309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a79",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若把这件事透露给萨拉议长、或许就能借{00}此强化我们的立场",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e81be7b9e991efb8ed10e858e839e83be7c2e8e3ef3402e905e8a7e7c5e7c6eadc00e7cae8ade9a5efcce7bbe7b4e86be8760000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ab6",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可那样做、恐怕会让他们父子二人彻底决{00}裂啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b7e7dae81c02eb33e958e7e2e7f9e80ce7bbe888e886ea13efb2ebc5e9b4e8ab00ec3ae7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1af5",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "事到如今已顾不上手段了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb8e7d7e7f0efb9ef3aea1fe7b5ef4cef66ea6be7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b11",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要想强化特列斯阁下的立场、就必须牵制{00}住阿兹拉埃尔",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7e6e8ade9a5e7cfe8b5e7c8e8d7ef4de7b4e86be87602e7c5e860e9a2eb94e8de00e859e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e10000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b4f",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "特列斯阁下的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cfe8b5e7c8e8d7ef4de7b409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b91",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……原来如此、这条情报确实有用",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8e4efcfe7f0e7ca02e7b9e9d4e88be913e88ce87fe7cbefb30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bd5",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……阿斯兰、你可真叫我失望透了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d2e7c8e86f02e7b8e7c4e820e8c1efcce8a5e965ed10e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1be6",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你不仅擅自抛下了交派给你的任务、竟还{00}去帮那些自然人……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b5eb7aeb5defb5eaa9ef4de7bae861e985e839e7b8e7b4e89ae94f02ef2ce7f700e7ebe910e7b7e8a4efb5e7efefb20909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c2c",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……父亲、对于这场战争、您究竟是怎么{00}看的？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e888e89402e7bee879e7b9e876ef28e85202e835e906ef2ce7b6e7f2e7bd00e7f6e7b4050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c5f",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是在要你给我解释！哪有空理会这种无{00}聊问题……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6ef29ef2ae7b8e839efcce89dec9fef97e8ffe7cbe93fe872e7e2e7b9e7d1e7dc00ec36e997ea1209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c9f",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这绝不是什么无聊的问题！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e91ce7b5e7b6e7dde7bde7dcec36e7b4e997ea12ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cb0",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "被打了就还手、还手又挨打！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f1e7f5e7bae7c5e7f7ef6602e7f7ef66e8f1eb8ae7f5ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cce",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这种反复、要持续到几时才完！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7d1e87ce9ee02ef2ae9efe9ade7d7eaa5ef2de836e87eef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d09",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你到底是从哪儿、学来了这种荒唐至极的{00}念头！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7d7e9b4e7b6e88ae8ffeb7c02eb55efcfe7bae7b9e7d1ec38edf7e897eacae7b400ea27e92eef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d3f",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这是我自己的想法！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7b6efccefb5e8c9e7b4e7e6e84eef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d4d",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "光是凭力与力一味地硬碰硬……",
   "zh_hex": "15e83de7b6ea49efb0e832efb0efb6ed36ef63eb97eb98eb9709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d5e",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您当真认为、那样下去就能真正结束这场{00}战争吗、父亲！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835ef53e820e8a0e7c102e7b7e7daef4de7ebe7c5e7c6e820ef3be868e895e7b9e87600ef28e852e80202e888e894ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d9c",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "当然能结束！只要把自然人统统消灭干净{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef53e7efe7c6e868e895ef97ef32ef2ae81befb5e7efefb2e929e929e928e8e1e8d3ecb000ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dcc",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……父亲！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e888e894ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e22",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……说啊、阿斯兰、自由和正义高达、如{00}今到哪儿去了？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7ede7c302e7d2e7c8e86f02efb5e8a6e7d3ef3be8cee812ef2b02e7f000efb9e7d7e8ffeb7ce7ebe7ba050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e37",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "视你的回答而定、我也可以把你当成叛逆{00}者抓起来",
   "zh_hex": "15e9d9e7b8e7b4ef52ea96e89ce86702efcce7c0e7c4e7f3e81be7b8ef53e837ef43eeb400ef6ee962e847efcf0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e71",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "父、父亲……",
   "zh_hex": "15e88802e888e89409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e8f",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e90",
   "jp_len": 81,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001060c02136e183302000106c6001316173302000106030006c6001333173302000206190006c60013ef173302000215e7beefb5e8c9e7b4e894ef8deb7ce886e81ce7d7e7b9e7d1ef63ea9302efcce7f6e7c400e7b5e86aee05ef53e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1efb",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……萨拉议长",
   "zh_hex": "150909e83be7c2e8e3ef340000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f1c",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f1d",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001060402136e183302000106c5001316173302000115e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f6f",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哎哟！还是请你别轻举妄动为好",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dceb2cef97e7f7e7b6e83ae7b8e7e5e990ea21ecc6ef30e7c1e7c70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f9f",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、你是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7b8e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fc4",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "安德鲁·巴尔特菲尔德",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fce82ce8a2ef4be85be7e1e7cfea6ce7e1e82c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fd0",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还是说、报上奇迹生还的沙漠之虎这名号{00}、你会更清楚？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7b6e7ed02e913ef4ce904ed0fef8de7f7e7b4eb0ceceae7cdec91e7b9e8ace8330002e7b8e7e2e952e995ebd3050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2009",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你这家伙……是受了拉克丝·克莱因的指{00}使吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd0909e7b6e8c8e7bae7c2e7d5e8a304e7d5e846ef33e7b4e8c000e83fe7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2038",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……拉克丝！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c2e7d5e8a3ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2062",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……受她所托",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8c8e88ee7fbe7f40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x206e",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是来救你的、阿斯兰",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6efcfe8cae7b8e7b402e7d2e7c8e86f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2095",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你能平安无事、真是太好了、阿斯兰",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c6e887e7fce7dcefb802e820e7b6e86ae7c7e7ba02e7d2e7c8e86f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20c7",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拉克丝……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c2e7d5e8a30909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20cf",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这里到底是什么地方……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef31e7d7e9b4e7b6e7dde7bdef63efb109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20e6",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20e7",
   "jp_len": 44,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001060502136e183302000106c60013161733020001150909e7b9e7b6eb09eb1de7bae8f3ef30efb0e7b4efa7ef9ee986efb3e9d5e7d40200e9bfeb85e8330000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2113",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这次起飞会有点猛、还请你多担待些",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e864e847ea45e7e2e7cbe822ed8702e7f7e83ae7b8e7e9e9fdeaa8e8a40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2146",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没关系",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e8bbe9410000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2150",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们非走不可",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe8f0e890e7b5e7c40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2166",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2167",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b3302000115e9bfeb85e83302e83ae86be91fe847ea45ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21bd",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿斯兰·萨拉？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e7c8e86fef4be83be7c2050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21e2",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……啊、是！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c302e7b6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21ec",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『阿斯兰·萨拉与拉克丝·克莱因、乘新{00}型舰一同逃走……』",
   "zh_hex": "150ce7d2e7c8e86f04e83be7c2e832e7c2e7d5e8a304e7d5e846ef3302ebb1ef8a00e977e7d487e85de8c2e89009090d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2209",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "目前、扎夫特军内部通信往来十分频繁",
   "zh_hex": "15d5ba02e84be830e7cfe7e0e99accc2e90fe911d9ea4acdeec6eda100000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2240",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿斯兰和拉克丝他们……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e7c8e86fe7d3e7c2e7d5e8a3e80ce7bb09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2266",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、现在情况怎么样了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e82fef29e88be8d0e7f2e7bde7dae7ba050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x228c",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "PLANT那边似乎已经派出追击部队",
   "zh_hex": "15eed4e81aea9ceed3eed6e7b7e899e944e933ef3ae8b7e985afe8dde7cccce7c90000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22bf",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再怎么说是新型舰、那里也是扎夫特的眼{00}皮子底下吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7f2e7bde7ede7b6ef8ae977e7d402e7b7ef31e7c0e7b6e84be830e7cfe7b4e90b00ebdde886e9b489e7d005000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22d9",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "想要彻底逃出去、可没那么简单",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e6ef2aebc5e9b4e8c2efbee7eb02e7c4e7d8e7b7e7bde9abe9180000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2303",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们不能就这样见死不救！去救他们吧、{00}克瓦特罗大尉！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b5e7c6e7c5e7b9e7dae85cef6ae7b5e8caef97e7ebe8cae80ce7bbe7d00200e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2340",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、正如穆少佐指出的、那里可是扎夫{00}特的大本营",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602ef3be7f0eb10efacefbae8c0efbee7b402e7b7ef31e7c4e7b6e84be83000e7cfe7b4efa5efa6ed010000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x235c",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "弄不好、我们也会……",
   "zh_hex": "15eac4e7b5e7c702efcce7bbe7c0e7e209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2385",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……若是这件事、或许我能帮上各位一点{00}忙",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7e7e7b6e7b9e991efb802e905e8a7efcce7c6e910ef4ce819e834efb6e82200ea060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23b7",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "迪安娜女王！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ea11e7fce7eaefade884ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23db",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为了与各位会合、我特意率领一部分迪安{00}娜回归军赶来了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7bae832e819e834e7e2efc002efcce7cfef3ce9e1ea20efb6ef70efaeea11e7fc00e7eaef52e947e7e0ea04efcfe7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23ff",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我想、我们有足够的战力、从扎夫特手里{00}救出那位叫阿斯兰的人",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7e602efcce7bbe7cbea1ee920e7b4ef28efb002e88ae84be830e7cfef66ef3100e8caefbee7b7e834e8c1e7d2e7c8e86fe7b4efb20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x243c",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那……真是求之不得的提议、不过、这样{00}真的好吗、女王？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b70909e820e7b6e93ae7cde7b5e80ae7b4e821e8e302e7b5ef3602e7b9e7da00e820e7b4e7c7e80202efade884050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2457",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明明月之民那边、都还没从先前的那场混{00}乱中脱身呢",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39ef39e850e7cdef38e7b7e89902e840e7f7e7d8e88aef8bef51e7b4e7b7e876ea4100e976ef4ee9e5e88de9070000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2492",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我认为、首先要做的、是平定地球圈的这{00}场战乱",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8a0e7c102ef40ef8bef2ae81ce7b402e7b6e887e867ef63efd3e9fbe7b4e7b900e876ef28e9760000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24b5",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再说、月球那边的事、我也已经托付给琪{00}耶尔小姐了",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7ed02e850efd3e7b7e899e7b4efb802efcce7c0ef3ae8b7e7f4e97ee839efa100ea31e7e1e83ee921e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24f0",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "琪耶尔·海姆小姐她！？",
   "zh_hex": "15efa1ea31e7e1ef4be91be823e83ee921e88eef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2518",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "她正代替我统管月之民",
   "zh_hex": "15e88eef3be8e7ea50efcce929e93be850e7cdef380000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2533",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、关于月之民那边、还请各位尽管放{00}心",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302e8bbe879e850e7cdef38e7b7e89902e7f7e83ae819e834e8f2e93be86c00e82d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2563",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那就这么定了、克瓦特罗大尉",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7c5e7b9e7bde867e7ba02e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2573",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就向PLANT进发、把他们救出来吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c59deed4e81aea9ceed3eed6e892e87002e81be80ce7bbe8caafd9e7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25a1",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……说得对",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7ede80ae7be0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25e9",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "原来如此……大天使号是朝PLANT方向去{00}了吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e4d9e7f0e7ca0909bee844e83fe833e7b6eaadeed4e81aea9ceed3eed6d09de7eb00e7bae8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2626",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b606000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2655",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么一来、扎夫特那边恐怕也不会太平了{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bdefb6efcf02e84be830e7cfe7b7e899eb33e958e7c0e7b5e7e2e86ae887e7ba0009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x266b",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……看来、我们该登场的时刻、终于到了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f6efcf02efcce7bbe898e9a0e876e7b4ef2de91f02e8e2e879e7d7e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64da",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……怎么样、梅丽贝尔？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f2e7bde7da02e9f2e9c5e857e7e1050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6507",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感觉不错哦、基姆！",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8aee7b5e885e91902e829e823ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x653a",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "∀吗……作为一份见面礼、这可阔气得过{00}头了",
   "zh_hex": "15effee8020909ef2fe7c1efb6ea22e85ce862eb6502e7b9e7c4eec0e8ede80aef3600e92ee7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6572",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可尽管如此、金卡拉姆阁下您看上去却不{00}怎么高兴啊？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e8f2e93be7f0e7ca02e902e801e7c2e823e8d7ef4de835e7f6ef4ce7ebeadfe7b500e7f2e7bde812eabae7c3050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x65ad",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一仗都没打、就把敌方最重要的一张底牌{00}弄到了手、自然觉得扫兴",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6ea37e840e7d8e7f502e7c5e81be7e3efb1e8c5e8a1ef2ae7b4efb6eac5e9b4ec2b00eac4e7d7e7baef6602efb5e7efe8aee80aeb88eaba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x65ef",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这就是政治、阁下",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7c5e7b6ea68ea7902e8d7ef4d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x661c",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哼",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x663e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "恕我直言",
   "zh_hex": "15eb04efcce875efd70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x664c",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金卡拉姆舰队虽说具备了充足的战力、不{00}过……",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e801e7c2e823e7d4e7c9e8b8e7edea14e877e7baea86ea1ee7b4ef28efb002e7b500ef3609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6664",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可在这类方面、似乎就有些考虑不够周到{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4ef29e7b9e841efb1e86202e944e933e7c5e7cbe8a4eb41eba1e7b5e920ea5ce7d700e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x66a0",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是说、要由你来填补我们所欠缺的政治{00}手腕？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e7ed02ef2ae8a6e7b8efcfee01ea81efcce7bbe7fbee44ee81e7b4ea68ea7900ef66ee8e050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x66cf",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我愿尽一份微薄之力、助金卡拉姆阁下成{00}就霸业",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce961e8f2efb6ea22eb58ee97e7cdefb002ea23e902e801e7c2e823e8d7ef4de83700e7c5eefdeada0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6708",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好个小小的谋士……！你是打算把我也拉{00}拢过去吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e828e83ee83ee7b4ea6eef640909ef97e7b8e7b6e7f5e889e81befcce7c0e7c200ed65ef36e7ebe802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x673b",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那点小把戏对您行不通、这我也心里有数",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e822e83ee81bea3ee7bee835efd6e7b5ef5902e7b9efcce7c0e82def31e7cbe9140000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6759",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我只想借阁下之手、成就我所坚信的理想{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef32e7e6eadce8d7ef4de7cdef6602e837e7c5efcce7fbeb80e90fe7b4e872e7e60009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6778",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这便是我毫不掩饰的真心话",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e8fae7b6efccea0ae7b5ec72eec8e7b4e820e82de81f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x67aa",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哼、也好、就先拿你来利用一番吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b302e7c0e7c702e7c5b8e9a7e7b8d9e82ed887ee6de7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x67de",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多谢您、阁下",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9e8b2e83502e8d7ef4d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6802",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "梅丽贝尔！热身也差不多该结束了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f2e9c5e857e7e1ef97ead1e88de7c0e9c7e7b5e7e9e898e868e895e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6814",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今∀与倒X这两台机体都已到手、是时{00}候行动了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efb9effee832e848eed9e7b9e97dea16e7e4ef4fe840ef3ae7d7ef6602e7b6ef2d00ea39efd6ef30e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x686f",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "御大将！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec68efa5e84aef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6894",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了？是那帮叫奥古的追上来了吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba05e7b6e7b7e910e8c1e82be84de7b4e8ddef4cefcfe7bae802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x68c3",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、不是！并非奥古！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7b5e7b6ef97e957e8f0e82be84def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x68d7",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一艘战舰、几台MS！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6eb18ef28e7d402eaa5ea16efa7ef9eef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x68e6",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对方是宇宙海盗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beefb1e7b6e8bee8bfe91be9f3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x691a",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夺取∀高达！！X1立即出击！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea17e987effee812ef2bef97ef97eed9eff7e86be855efbee7ccef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x698e",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就是那台叫∀的高达吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7b6e7b7ea16e8c1effee7b4e812ef2be80209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x69ca",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好！金凯度·纳乌、这就出击！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c7ef97e902e95fe96def4be882e94d02e7b9e7c5efbee7ccef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a0f",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a21",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a22",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001063c00136e1833020001061b001316173302000115e83be825e896ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a4d",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a4e",
   "jp_len": 54,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001064b00136e1833020001062200131617330200010603000622001333173302000215e83dea49e7b8efb6e828efb202e958e7b6e7e2ea06e7b5ef36efcfe7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a8f",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a90",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001063c00136e1833020001061b0013161733020001150909e9fa02e9a1e7b8e7b4e8fae7d0ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ac3",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ac4",
   "jp_len": 64,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001064b00136e1833020001062200131617330200010603000622001333173302000215ef3def3d02e7e8e7e8e7e80909ef97e7b7e7b6ef53e7ef02efcce7c5e7b5eccb00e8edef63efcee8c8e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b37",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（这可不行啊……怎能让贝拉大人在这种{00}地方栽跟头！）",
   "zh_hex": "150ae7b9e7c4e7b59fe7c30909e7f2e7c6e7f9e857e7c2beb4ef29e7b9e7d100bfd0ec5de973e92e060b00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b7e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "御、御大将！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec6802ec68efa5e84aef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ba4",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "磨磨蹭蹭的干什么！既是敌人、就给我快{00}准备开战！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec81ec81ec98ec98e7b4e8d3e7dde7bdef97e8c4e7b6e7e3efb202e7c5e839efcce85f00e87ae877e7faef28ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6be0",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可、可是、对付海盗的作战模拟、我们还{00}没做过啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c402e7c4e7b602e7bee97ee91be9f3e7b4ef2fef28ea91ebc902efcce7bbe7f700e7d8e81cef36e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c0f",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么都照着手册一板一眼地办、那是蠢货{00}才会干的事！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bde840ea1ae86def66ede2efb6ed75efb6e90bef63e8ea02e7b7e7b6e94beaf500e836e7e2e8d3e7b4efb8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c2c",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "快给我把MS派出去！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e85fe839efcce81befa7ef9ee985efbee7ebef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c62",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "少爷",
   "zh_hex": "15b1ed85000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c84",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "当着基姆·金卡拉姆的面、我们也有必要{00}展露一下实力",
   "zh_hex": "15ef53e86de829e823ef4be902e801e7c2e823e7b4e86202efcce7bbe7c0e7cbe860ef2a00e989e858efb6ef4de87fefb00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ca0",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们也前进！威尔盖姆号、准备对MS战{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "158be7bbe7c0bae89206e96be7e1ec7ee823e83302e87ae877e7be1314ef2800060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6cda",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "冲过来了吗……那也好",
   "zh_hex": "15e95eef36efcfe7bae8020909e7b7e7c0e7c70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ceb",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就让我亲眼见识见识、传闻中那些未来{00}人的战力！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7f9efcce894e90be85ce92fe85ce92f02ea38ebacef4ee7b7e8a4e8b4efcf00efb2e7b4ef28efb0ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d36",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……扎比涅！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e84be825eacf06000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d3e",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瞄准那台叫∀的MS的动力部、一举打得{00}它动弹不得！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea30e87ae7b7ea16e8c1effee7b4efa7ef9ee7b4ef30efb0ef7002efb6ea21e7f5e80a00e978ef30e946e7b5e80aef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d7f",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明白",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef39e8090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6dae",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好……上！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c70909ef4cef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6dde",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夺取∀高达！！X1、X2立即出击！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea17e987effee812ef2bef97ef97eed9eff702eed9ef5fe86be855efbee7ccef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e3c",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81d050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e6a",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "咦？萨、扎比涅先生？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef4905e83b02e84be825eacfb8b60500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e98",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……这不是金凯度！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b9e7b5e7b6e902e95fe96def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6eca",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我在这里",
   "zh_hex": "150909efccef29e7b9ef310000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6edf",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ee0",
   "jp_len": 45,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001064b00136e1833020001062200131617330200010603000622001333173302000215e90202e902e95fe96def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f18",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f19",
   "jp_len": 52,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001063c00136e1833020001061b001316173302000115e981e7b5ec1302efcce7bee7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd02e7c4e7d8e7b7e7bde90fe80aef360000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f4d",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉的护卫、就由我来负责",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2e7b4e8e0e9b202e7c5e8a6efccefcfe92ceba60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fbe",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……托比亚！那个长胡子的、就是我们的{00}目标！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f4e825e7d606e7b7e828ef34ec8be886e7b402e7c5e7b68be7bbe7b400d5e96f06000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fd2",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用X3一击废掉它的动力部……办得到吧{00}！？",
   "zh_hex": "15efb3eed9ef60efb6e7cceae5e9d3e978e7b4ef30efb0ef700909e8eae80ae7d7e7d000ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7016",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是！我会想办法试试看！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6ef97efcce7e2e7e6e8eae84ee91de91de7f6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7052",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3e7c3ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x708a",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "糟了！……贝拉！！",
   "zh_hex": "15eeafe7ba060909e857e7c2060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70ca",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是什么东西！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e7dde7bde8bae7f8ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70f2",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70f3",
   "jp_len": 52,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001063501136e1833020001067a001316173302000115e7c4e7de02e7b6e850e83dea03e802ef97e7b9e910e7c4e9bee7b4e91be9f3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x714a",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "绝不能让威尔盖姆号沉没！米哈埃尔大佐、{00}快后退！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e91ce7b5e7c6e7f9e96be7e1ec7ee823e833e983e7d806e878e7e8e96ae7e1bea30200e85fe7fee88006060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7196",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这家伙！到底想干什么啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7dfe7fdef97e7d7e9b4e7e6e8d3e7dde7bde7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71ce",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就是现在！快回收∀！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b6e82fef29ef97e85fef52e926effeef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7206",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！下次见面绝不饶你！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de0689e864e85ce862e91ce7b5eab5e7b806000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7246",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "区区一两只海盗罢了！！正好拿来给∀热{00}身、是个不错的对手！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef35ef35efb6e97def32e91be9f3eaefe7baef97ef97ef3be7c7e9a7efcfe839effeead100e88d02e7b6e828e7b5e885e7b4e7beef66ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x728d",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "光是仗着机体的性能、可休想打倒我这个{00}金凯度！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e83de7b6ea37e86de7e4ef4fe7b4e951e7c602e7c4e90ee7e6e7f5e848efcce7b9e82800e902e95fe96def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x72d2",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵、呵呵……哈哈哈……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3d02ef3def3d0909e7e8e7e8e7e809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x72df",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这都是为了贝拉大人……那台MS、我就{00}收下了、女人！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e840e7b6e7c1e7bae857e7c2efa5efb20909e7b7ea16efa7ef9e02efcce7c500e926ef4de7ba02efadefb2ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x731c",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这、这家伙……！？真是个叫人发毛的对{00}手！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b902e7b9e7dfe7fd0909ef9705e820e7b6e828e8c1efb2e870eb60e7b4e7be00ef66ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x735e",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瞄准动力部、一击就封住它的行动……",
   "zh_hex": "15ea30e87aef30efb0ef7002efb6e7cce7c5eb83e859e978e7b4efd6ef3009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7375",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "上吧、托比亚！！",
   "zh_hex": "15b2e7d002e7f4e825e7d606060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73a2",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "同样是高达、我这台可不一样！臭小子给{00}我滚一边去！",
   "zh_hex": "15e85de7dae7b6e812ef2b02efcce7b9ea16e7c4e7b5efb6e7daef97ecfde83ee886e83900efccece8efb6e899e7ebef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73e6",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "高达上竟画着骷髅标记、真是大胆包天啊{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e812ef2bef4cef2cecefe86dedcdedcfe96fe99602e820e7b6efa5edaeeabbe844e7c300ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7400",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要不要就这么把你压扁、碾成碎片啊——{00}！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b5ef2ae7c5e7b9e7bde81be7b8e992ee2802ed95e837ebe0ee5ee7c3ebafebaf00ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7443",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "比起月之民、那家伙的作风、反倒更像我{00}们这边的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e825e847e850e7cdef3802e7b7e7dfe7fde7b4ef2feb7502e87ce848e952e8e98b00e7bbe7b9e899e7b40909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7482",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！区区海盗之流！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de06ef35ef35e91be9f3e7cdea2e06060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x74ba",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就是敌方的主将吗……动手吧、扎比涅{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7b6e7e3d0e7b4e954e84ae8020909ef30aee7d002e84be825eacf000606000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x753a",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x756a",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那就是敌方的首领吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7c5e7b6e7e3efb1e7b4ef40ea20e8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x758b",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x758c",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001068f00136e183302000106420013161733020001150909e83be825e896ef8bef8def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75d6",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……他自己退走了吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e80cefb5e8c9e880e890e7bae8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75e2",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要是真刀真枪地打起来、会是什么结果…{00}…想想都直冒冷汗",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b6e820ed25e820eaaebfe7f5e847d902e7e2e7b6e7dde7bde868e871090009e7e6e7e6e840e875eb7feb4eee4a00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x90c2",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "冲过来了吗……有趣！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e95eef36efcfe7bae8020909e7cbea82ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9102",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……什么——！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dde7bdebafebafef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x912a",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x912b",
   "jp_len": 51,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b33020001063501136e1833020001067a001316173302000115e7dde7bdef97ef97e866e82ae7b9e7c5e7b60909eb35e7cbeb45e851e7b4e97be8e900ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x918e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……呵呵",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef3def3d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x91c6",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！可、可恶啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7c402e7c4e7dee7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9206",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……就是现在！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c5e7b6e82fef29ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x923e",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎、怎么可能！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f202e7f2e7bde7c4e7c6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x927a",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼、哼哈哈……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b302e8b3e7e8e7e809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9288",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x9289",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b3302000115e82fef29e7c4e7b5efd6e7c30909e7c4e7b5e7c6e7f9e7b8e97fe8c6e7bae857e7c200efa5efb20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x92ad",
   "jp_len": 1,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "bf"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x92ae",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "1b3302000115e7dce8dce7beef66e7b6e923ef97e8ffe958e7b6e89aefbcefb2ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x92f6",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那种程度的玩意、对倒X根本不管用！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7d1ea7de96de7b4e970ef3c02e7bee848eed9e9b8efa6e7b5e93befb3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x933a",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们这边的攻击、可还没结束呢！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b9e899e7b4ef67e7cc02e7c4e7f7e7d8e868e895e907ef97ef970000"
  }
 ]
